These are Puzzles for 1x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-1::.
There are 4 different nationalities: canadian, pakistani, spanish, japanese
1. the pakistani is in an odd position##4
2. the japanese is between the canadian and the pakistani##2
3. the japanese is on the right of the canadian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |    3    |  4   |
| Nationality   | canadian | japanese | pakistani | spanish |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-2::.
There 4 different types of food: grapefruit, kale, spinach, apple
1. the person eating grapefruit is on the left of the person eating apple##1
2. the person eating kale is in an odd position##4
3. the person eating kale is on the left or right of the person eating grapefruit##3

.:: Answer ::.
|        |   1    |    2    |   3    |   4   |
| Food   | kale | grapefruit | apple | spinach |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-3::.
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, scientific, superhero, satire
1. the person watching satire movies is on the left or right of the person watching fantasy movies##3
2. the person watching fantasy movies is in an odd position##4
3. the person watching superhero movies is between the person watching satire movies and the person watching scientific movies##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2    |    3    |      4       |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | satire | superhero | scientific |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-4::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, parkour, surfing, rowing
1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left or right of the person who's sport is badminton##3
2. the person who's sport is surfing is in an even position##4
3. the person who's sport is rowing is between the person who's sport is badminton and the person who's sport is surfing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1       |    2     |       3       |   4    |
| Sport   | parkour | badminton | rowing | surfing |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-5::.
