1. the person who's sport is climbing is in an even position##4
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
3. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cricket##3

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |    2     |    3    |    4     |
| Sport   | biathlon | climbing | cricket | snowboarding |

