.:: Puzzle 1x4-Level-4-6::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, australian, turkish, argentine
1. the australian is on the far right##1
2. the australian is on the left or right of the argentine##3
3. the turkish is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |  3   |    4    |
| Nationality   | turkish | dutch | argentine | australian |

