1. the fan of blues is on the left or right of the fan of country##3
2. the fan of indie is between the fan of country and the fan of hip-hop##2
3. the fan of indie is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |  1   |   2   |  3  |  4   |
| Music-Genre   | blues | country | indie | hip-hop |

