2. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the left or right of the person who's sport is cycling##3
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is on the left or right of the person who's sport is rowing##3
4. the person who's sport is rowing is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |    3     |   4   |
| Sport   | ice-hockey | rowing | cycling | volleyball |

