2. the person eating asparagus is on the left or right of the person eating radish##3
3. the person eating radish is on the far left or far right##3
4. the person eating papaya is in an even position##4
5. the person eating asparagus is on the left of the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1     |     2      |   3   |    4    |
| Food   | radish | asparagus | pear | papaya |

